

1) export the sam and system files using powershell to current location:

reg save HKLM\sam ./sam
reg save HKLM\system ./system

2) from kali/wsl2 (in the saved directory):
apt update -y
apt install python3-impacket -y
impacket-secretsdump -sam sam -system system LOCAL > hashes.txt


